{"tid":1074670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果CEO Tim Cook：感謝中國","createTime":"2019-03-23T14:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T15:16:27.000Z","uid":1369,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00dc89ea90a7e5bf41d64348cea550aab530636c","tid":1074670,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"【蘋果CEO庫克：感謝中國打開了大門，我們未來密不可分】＃蘋果CEO感謝中國＃3月23日，蘋果公司CEO蒂姆&middot;庫克在＃中國發展高層論壇＃上說，蘋果公司作為全球社區的一員，需要共同合作，共同攜手來改變世界，蘋果非常感謝中國能夠打開市場大門，讓我們成為一份子。我們的未來是密不可分的。蘋果公司期待中國在未來不斷地開放。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vhx7aCv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvhx7aCv.png&h=fe6c2c08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f471d6ac39040efa4c7b23ca58e17fd9d71ab2e8","tid":1074670,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:28:51.000Z","msg":"從來未試過咁想一個人死<br />\n呢條Gay Cock真係第一個"},{"pid":"002cfde08f75064ee6d167b14a137bdeeb45eed5","tid":1074670,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"奶呀奶呀"},{"pid":"dcd0c6bfe664fb0791e168b37574aa303b915d7d","tid":1074670,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc9b88d2cc4a1ea34c7d3daa8c4b599fb57a495","tid":1074670,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:16:01.000Z","msg":"呢頭同完Donald Trump 吹水，轉頭就去奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da36eb620682b5b505844c44da3969b4c15a5c7","tid":1074670,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:16:27.000Z","msg":"tim china"}]}